trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>, specifying the concrete MIME type for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: 表示可扩展性元素添加到<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"> </xref>，指定具体的 MIME 类型<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>到<xref uid="langword_csharp_MimePart" name="MimePart" href=""></xref>适用。

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: 有关指定的 XML Web 服务协议的详细信息，请参阅[[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices&1;>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 有关 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL) 的详细信息，请参阅在 http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/ 规范。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> class.

Gets the collection of MIME extensibility elements for the part of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref> of which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref> is a member.
trans-unit.target: 获取的部分的 MIME 可扩展性元素的集合<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding"></xref>其中<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>是成员。

trans-unit.source: This collection must have at least one member.
trans-unit.target: 此集合必须具有至少一个成员。

trans-unit.source: If it has more than one member, the members are alternative MIME formats for the current <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>.
trans-unit.target: 如果它具有多个成员，成员是当前<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>替代 MIME 格式

trans-unit.source: Members can be of the following types: - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding> - <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding> Each of these classes exposes a `Part` property specifying the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> with which the `MimePart` is associated.
trans-unit.target: 成员可以是以下类型:- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding>- <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding>-<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding>其中每个类公开`Part`属性指定<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>与其`MimePart`关联。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBodyBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding>

trans-unit.source: If this collection has no members, the XML Web service will fail to generate a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) file when it is requested.
trans-unit.target: 如果此集合没有任何成员，XML Web 服务将无法生成 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL) 文件，它请求时。

trans-unit.source: For more information about how MIME extends WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 有关如何 MIME 扩展 WSDL 的详细信息，请参阅 http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/ 的规范。

trans-unit.source: A collection of service description format extension.
trans-unit.target: 服务说明格式扩展的集合。
